  "customHelp": "(1) To Recycle a card, hold Shift while dragging the card to its deck.\n(2) You can create Tokens and Buffs with right click on the source card.\n(3) You can mark buffed units and Damage/Might mods with 'C + click' and 'Ctrl + C + click'. Otherwise, you can Group (attach) a Buff card to another with the right-click menu.\n(4) To play a Hidden card, use Z + click on a card on your hand and then move it to the Battlefield. Then do the same to reveal it.\n(5) You can mark your points at the bottom left.",
